,CASE WHEN Edad_Reg BETWEEN 0 AND 29 AND Tipo_Edad='D'  THEN '0 A 29 DIAS'WHEN (Edad_Reg BETWEEN 0 AND 29 AND Tipo_Edad='D') OR (Tipo_Edad='M' AND Edad_Reg=1 )   THEN '29 A 59 DIAS' WHEN (Tipo_Edad='M' AND Edad_Reg BETWEEN 2 AND 11 )   THEN '2 A 11 MESES' WHEN (Tipo_Edad='A' AND Edad_Reg BETWEEN 1 AND 4 )   THEN '1 A 4 AÑOS' WHEN (Tipo_Edad='A' AND Edad_Reg BETWEEN 5 AND 11 )   THEN '5 A 11 AÑOS'END  GRUPO_EDAD FROM rpt_plano_cbeta_acum 
